7
00:00:32,259 --> 00:00:33,660
Why have you been hiding?

8
00:00:33,940 --> 00:00:36,470
Do you know
who was at the fighting ring today?

9
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,570
Are you blaming me

10
00:00:50,910 --> 00:00:52,240
