24
00:01:30,950 --> 00:01:32,390
or what rules to follow.

25
00:01:33,140 --> 00:01:34,590
Why have you completely changed

26
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:35,700
after meeting that woman?

27
00:01:35,700 --> 00:01:36,670
Even after I hurt her sister,

28
00:01:36,670 --> 00:01:38,670
