29
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:42,910
Jinzhi.

30
00:01:45,390 --> 00:01:46,259
I'm sorry.

31
00:01:48,610 --> 00:01:50,450
I truly can't give you anything.

32
00:01:59,910 --> 00:02:00,940
I know.

33
00:02:03,730 --> 00:02:05,730
Sometimes, I just can't understand

34
00:02:10,259 --> 00:02:12,950
why I love you so much,

35
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:17,620
and why I'm willing
to humble myself like this,

36
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:20,400
still hoping you might love me just once.

37
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:23,790
I'm a bastard.

38
00:02:25,950 --> 00:02:27,740
I don't deserve to be loved.

39
00:02:28,579 --> 00:02:29,740
Since your father has passed away,

40
00:02:29,740 --> 00:02:30,910
