41
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,590
Leave the Thunder Gang.

42
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:40,910
On the table, there's a bankbook

43
00:02:41,450 --> 00:02:42,820
with all my money in it.

44
00:02:45,370 --> 00:02:47,210
Take it and enjoy your life.

45
00:03:16,410 --> 00:03:17,579
Yin Huanyuan.

46
00:03:19,420 --> 00:03:20,829
Remember this.

47
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:24,270
Today, it's not you
who are driving me away.

48
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:37,360
I, Xiao Jinzhi, am the one

49
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:43,640
who's going to

50
00:03:44,980 --> 00:03:47,329
cut all ties with you.

