68
00:05:13,170 --> 00:05:14,170
And that star

69
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:15,460
is my mother.

70
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:18,820
She's always circling around

71
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:21,380
my father and my sister.

72
00:05:33,090 --> 00:05:34,090
Then that star...

73
00:05:34,730 --> 00:05:35,990
That star is my mother.

74
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:38,180
The little stars around her

75
00:05:39,260 --> 00:05:40,050
are the children

76
00:05:40,050 --> 00:05:42,250
who were with her during the explosion.

77
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:47,090
Your mother is so beautiful and radiant.

78
00:05:50,610 --> 00:05:52,500
Hello, Mrs. Yin!

79
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:54,409
Don't worry,

80
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,440
Yin Zhuofeng is doing well.

81
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:58,460
He's quite impressive now.

82
00:06:01,340 --> 00:06:02,530
Yi!

83
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:05,580
You also don't need to worry.

84
00:06:07,170 --> 00:06:08,610
Now I'm also

85
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,280
doing well

86
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:11,900
and quite impressive.

87
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:18,020
I miss you so much.

88
00:06:56,210 --> 00:06:57,409
Do you remember this?

89
00:06:58,290 --> 00:06:59,260
Your stars.

90
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:01,580
