115
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:41,220
♪ I slowly pushed you away, but now
the regret is resolved in our reunion ♪

116
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:45,450
♪ I want to wait
until we grow old together ♪

117
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:48,210
♪ Then we can fill in the love we missed ♪

118
00:10:48,420 --> 00:10:53,560
♪ I want to hold you in my arms again ♪

119
00:10:53,770 --> 00:10:57,190
♪ I won't let you go again ♪

120
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:58,050
Be careful.

121
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,590
I have to hold my knife tightly.

122
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:11,810
I can't let go of it.

123
00:13:38,530 --> 00:13:39,620
Should I

124
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:43,020
open my eyes now
or keep pretending to be asleep?

125
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,090
Zhuofeng, are you sure...

126
00:13:51,690 --> 00:13:52,410
Zhuofeng.

127
00:13:53,980 --> 00:13:55,780
W-W-What's going on?

128
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:20,750
Zhuofeng, why are you smiling?

129
00:14:22,020 --> 00:14:22,950
I'm not smiling.

130
00:14:23,620 --> 00:14:25,020
You're clearly smiling.

131
00:14:25,260 --> 00:14:26,590
I'm really not smiling.

132
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:29,450
You've got serious issues.

133
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,410
Stop talking nonsense.

134
00:14:34,410 --> 00:14:35,340
Get to the point.

135
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:37,350
Yin Huanyuan, that bastard...

136
00:14:38,260 --> 00:14:38,980
That man.

137
00:14:39,290 --> 00:14:40,970
The information he gave is true.

138
00:14:40,970 --> 00:14:41,970
We did find

139
00:14:41,990 --> 00:14:43,380
traces of Yin Lei in Tang City.

140
00:14:43,380 --> 00:14:44,910
But we still need to confirm

141
00:14:44,930 --> 00:14:46,170
where he's hiding exactly.

142
00:14:46,170 --> 00:14:47,100
That guy

143
00:14:47,260 --> 00:14:48,450
is extremely cunning.

144
00:14:48,450 --> 00:14:49,380
Besides Yin Lei,

145
00:14:49,650 --> 00:14:51,510
do you have any news from Hai City?

146
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:54,580
Recently, there have been many officials
from Hai City going to Tang City.

147
00:14:54,580 --> 00:14:55,460
But strangely,

148
00:14:55,490 --> 00:14:56,810
their purpose was not for
official business.

149
00:14:56,810 --> 00:14:58,140
And they traveled

150
00:14:58,620 --> 00:15:00,220
in private vehicles.

151
00:15:00,810 --> 00:15:01,900
Yin Lei.

152
00:15:02,570 --> 00:15:03,570
Dancers.

153
00:15:04,740 --> 00:15:06,330
Hai City's officials.

154
00:15:07,170 --> 00:15:08,450
One Heart.

155
00:15:10,410 --> 00:15:12,220
Yin Lei is using dancers

156
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:13,990
to help One Heart

157
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:15,860
bribe Hai City's officials.

158
00:15:16,260 --> 00:15:18,650
One Heart is colluding
with the Thunder Gang

159
00:15:18,650 --> 00:15:19,810
to smuggle opium

160
00:15:20,330 --> 00:15:21,570
into Hai City.

161
00:15:28,050 --> 00:15:29,780
I've made some breakfast.

162
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:31,140
Come here and eat.

163
00:15:46,330 --> 00:15:47,530
Thank you, Zhuofeng.

164
00:15:52,930 --> 00:15:53,810
It's sweet.

165
00:15:55,220 --> 00:15:56,020
Lu Ye.

166
00:15:56,290 --> 00:15:57,620
Is this

167
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,110
your way of making up for

168
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:01,470
what you did last night?

169
00:16:03,980 --> 00:16:05,260
What did I do

170
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:08,690
last night?

171
00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:11,100
I can't remember anything.

172
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:16,420
I saw everything.

173
00:16:25,620 --> 00:16:27,140
You were drunk and acting wildly.

174
00:16:27,140 --> 00:16:29,980
You slept leaning on Zhuofeng all night.

175
00:16:33,380 --> 00:16:34,530
It's not a big deal.

176
00:16:34,780 --> 00:16:35,760
Something else happened, too.

177
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:36,890
What else happened?

178
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:37,690
You also...

179
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:50,470
You also smashed wine bottles everywhere.

180
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:52,800
Then I had to clean up
the mess all morning.

181
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:57,450
By the way, Lu Ye,

182
00:16:57,940 --> 00:16:59,610
after my brother bought back

183
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:00,570
this Lu family's old house,

184
00:17:00,570 --> 00:17:01,980
I've always been the one who cleans it.

185
00:17:01,980 --> 00:17:03,710
I finally got it all cleaned up,

186
00:17:04,089 --> 00:17:05,420
but you won't be staying long,

187
00:17:05,420 --> 00:17:06,950
and you'll be leaving soon.

188
00:17:13,020 --> 00:17:14,810
What's my next mission?

189
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:20,530
This time, One Heart is making a comeback

190
00:17:20,530 --> 00:17:22,420
to smuggle opium into Hai City.

191
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:25,020
For this purpose, they're colluding
with Yin Lei

192
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:27,329
to bribe Hai City's officials
with dancers.

193
00:17:27,329 --> 00:17:28,260
The location is

194
00:17:28,569 --> 00:17:30,570
the Golden Pleasure Club in Tang City.

195
00:17:30,570 --> 00:17:32,180
So my mission is to

196
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:33,740
pretend to be a dancer

197
00:17:33,890 --> 00:17:35,130
and infiltrate the Golden Pleasure Club?

198
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:35,930
That's right.

199
00:17:36,660 --> 00:17:38,660
We need to use these corrupt officials

200
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:40,810
to get the exact plan of smuggling opium

201
00:17:40,810 --> 00:17:43,810
and wait for the chance
to kill the leader of One Heart,

202
00:17:44,090 --> 00:17:44,940
the Priest.

203
00:17:46,610 --> 00:17:47,290
Lu Ye.

204
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,660
This mission

205
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,530
isn't like a battle in the fighting ring.

206
00:17:50,530 --> 00:17:51,730
There are no referees

207
00:17:52,050 --> 00:17:53,090
and no rules.

208
00:17:53,610 --> 00:17:54,810
Once you enter there,

209
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:57,510
you won't even have a chance to surrender.

210
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:02,330
At worst,

211
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,810
I'll end up like my sister.

212
00:18:05,660 --> 00:18:06,460
Right?

213
00:18:14,220 --> 00:18:15,420
There are such paths.

214
00:18:15,610 --> 00:18:17,540
Once you start the journey on them,

215
00:18:17,810 --> 00:18:19,470
there will be no turning back.

216
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,000
I won't look back.

217
00:18:22,590 --> 00:18:23,850
Because I have you guys

218
00:18:24,570 --> 00:18:25,460
behind me.

219
00:18:28,260 --> 00:18:29,780
It's time for me to become

220
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:31,130
a real dancer.

221
00:18:32,180 --> 00:18:32,890
Lu Ye.

222
00:18:33,370 --> 00:18:34,700
With your great talent,

223
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:36,340
there won't be any problems.

224
00:18:37,700 --> 00:18:39,420
Before you become a dancer,

225
00:18:40,610 --> 00:18:42,270
forget about all the missions

226
00:18:42,810 --> 00:18:44,130
and just be yourself for a day.
